Description: Native GTK4/libadwaita Slack client for the Linux desktop
 Sludge is a native GTK4/libadwaita Slack client. Features include real-time
 messaging via Socket Mode, inline threads, reactions, file uploads, desktop
 notifications, a GNOME Shell search provider, and fuzzy emoji autocomplete.
